<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">

  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">

         :labelCol="labelCol"

       </a-form-item>-->
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="用户id">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入用户id" v-decorator="['suserId', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="序号">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'iorder', {}]" />

      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="意见内容">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入意见内容" v-decorator="['scontent', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
